Title: An Act Changing the Name of Pooc Elementary School in the Municipality of Kalibo, Province of Aklan, to Honorable Jose M. Reyes Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 675
An Act Changing the Name of Pooc Elementary School in the Municipality of Kalibo, Province of Aklan, to Honorable Jose M. Reyes Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Pooc Elementary School in the Municipality of Kalibo, Province of Aklan, is changed to Honorable Jose M. Reyes Memorial Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
